Palatine bridge.
to the
Carmental gate, they may overtake us easily before we
reach the Campus. Aurelius has some errand to perform
near the Forum, which will detain us a few moments
longer
.
What say you?
He will come, he will come, certainly, cried the
other, springing down lightly from the back of his
beautiful
courser, which indeed merited the eulogium, as well as
the caresses which he now lavished on it, patting his
favorite's
high-arched neck, and stroking the soft velvet
