Phdon, Hortensia's Greek boy, brought it, noble
Paullus
.
He waits for your answer in the atrium.
Quick, then, quick, Thrasea, give me a reed and
paper
.
And snatching the materials he wrote hastily:
Chance only, evil chance, most lovely Julia, and
business
